              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Scattered protons were detected in the large-area",
                " segmented silicon detector array (SIDAR).SIDAR is",
                " comprised of 128 segments with 16 radial (from 5 to",
                " 13 cm) and 8 azimuthal divisions. The array covered",
                " laboratory angles 25deg -  51deg  allowing detection",
                " of the forward focused scattered protons while passing",
                " the 17F beam out of the target chamber."
              ]
